changes.content: // _data. We don't need to send any data for the bridging action.
// If the token being bridged is WETH then we need to first unwrap it to ETH and then send ETH over the
// canonical bridge. On Optimism, this is address 0xDeadDeAddeAddEAddeadDEaDDEAdDeaDDeAD0000.
// _l1Gas. Unused, but included for potential forward compatibility considerations
// _l2Token. Address of the L2 token to bridge over.
// _to. Withdraw, over the bridge, to the l1 pool contract.
